Author: beany_bag
Text: i think going to the dietician is a good idea. i get you cause i was like normal (i still had a shitty relationship with my body and stuff) but then all of a sudden a flip seemed to switch in my brain and i just went way overboard into proper disordered eating. i’d made myself throw up a few times before but i always convinced myself i was fine, it wasn’t proper purging or anything. now i’m terrified cause i don’t even care about schoolwork anymore i just care about losing weight
